zoom.setFactor.longDescription: For example, factor 0.5 would set the zoom factor to 50%, 1 would be 100% and 2 would be 200%.
zoom.setFactor.shortDescription: Set the zoom factor of the specified tab.

params.description: Tab to zoom with, of type `ui.models.tabSpace.Tab`.

zoom.getFactor.longDescription: For example, factor 0.5 would be a zoom factor at 50%, 1 would be 100% and 2 would be 200%.
zoom.getFactor.shortDescription: Get the zoom factor of the specified tab.
